{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So what had happened, as was explained to me, that this-- that these-- they had a firefight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The infantry did their thing, which is hide and shoot back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some of the SS surr-- tried to surrender.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they said, throw your arms down and come down out of the towers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they did, and they just shot them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "These infantry Americans just-- they probably were 30, 40, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they-- some of them still had their weapons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were still laying there, you know, but they-- but they were all-- they were all killed with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so that was that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then there was a moat where there were some SS bodies that had been-- evidently been thrown in the moat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now this is the day of liberation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we're still not in the main part of the camp yet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had just gone in to the-- to the train, which was not inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was on the perimeters-- and the towers, which we could get to from the outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, they were partly in and partly out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know what I'm saying?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We went back to the guar-- to the gates, and the guy wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We're going to stop this tape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
